10 多个坐标系显示¶

subplots

  • plt.subplots(nrows=1, ncols=1, **fig_kw) :axes(/)

    • Parameters
      • nrows,ncols:
      • **fig_kwfigure
    • Returns
      • fig:
      • axes
      • set_xticks
      • set_yticks
      • set_xlabel
      • set_ylabel

  • ''' ... ''',

In [11]:
# x,y
x = range(60)
y_shanghai = [np.random.uniform(15, 18) for _ in x]
y_beijing = [np.random.uniform(5, 10) for _ in x]

##################### New code #########################

# 
'''
plt.figure(figsize=(20,8),dpi=80)
'''
fig, axes = plt.subplots(nrows=1, ncols=2, figsize=(20, 8), dpi=100)

# 
'''
plt.plot(x, y_shanghai, label='')
'''
axes[0].plot(x, y_shanghai, label="")

# 
'''
plt.plot(x, y_beijing, color='r',linestyle='--',label='')
'''
axes[1].plot(x, y_beijing, color="r", linestyle="--", label="")

# x
x_ticks_label = ['11{}'.format(i) for i in x]

# y
y_ticks = range(40)

# xy
'''
plt.xticks(x[::5], x_ticks_label[::5])
plt.yticks(y_ticks[::5])
'''
axes[0].set_xticks(x[::5])
axes[0].set_yticks(y_ticks[::5])
axes[0].set_xticklabels(x_ticks_label[::5])
axes[1].set_xticks(x[::5])
axes[1].set_yticks(y_ticks[::5])
axes[1].set_xticklabels(x_ticks_label[::5])

# 
'''
plt.grid(True, linestyle='--', alpha=0.5)
'''
axes[0].grid(True, linestyle="--", alpha=0.5)
axes[1].grid(True, linestyle="--", alpha=0.5)

# xy
'''
plt.xlabel('')
plt.ylabel('')
plt.title('1112',fontsize=20)

'''
axes[0].set_xlabel("")
axes[0].set_ylabel("")
axes[0].set_title("11--12", fontsize=20)
axes[1].set_xlabel("")
axes[1].set_ylabel("")
axes[1].set_title("11--12", fontsize=20)

# 
'''
plt.legend(loc='best')'
'''
axes[0].legend(loc='best')
axes[1].legend(loc='best')

##################### New code #########################
Out[11]:
<matplotlib.legend.Legend at 0x1d589f4c708>

12.3 把图例放到图外显示¶

bbox_to_anchor

In [17]:
x = range(60)
y1 = [np.random.uniform(15, 18) for _ in x]
y2 = [np.random.uniform(10, 13) for _ in x]

# 
fig, ax = plt.subplots()

# label
ax.plot(x, y1, label='Group1')
ax.plot(x, y2, color='r', linestyle='--', label='Group2')

# 
ax.legend(loc='upper center', bbox_to_anchor=(0.5, 1.1), ncol=2)
Out[17]:
<matplotlib.legend.Legend at 0x1d58a481a08>
